Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:16.03,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A person I love?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:19.24,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Do you have someone special like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:21.29,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:24.87,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,My dad, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:28.50,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:32.34,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Rifana-chan?\N Do you have someone like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:35.17,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:39.05,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna marry someone like \None of the legendary heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:42.02,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Like the Shield Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:43.64,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna meet him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:55.15,flashback,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:05.36,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:07.08,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Spare my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:11.96,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,After you killed so many demi-humans \Nin your underground chamber,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:13.55,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,you think you can beg for your life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:16.51,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:20.01,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,One of those villagers \NI kept enslaved underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:21.64,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,One of those demis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:43.29,sign_3370_33_The_Rising_of_th,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,1)}The Rising of the Shield Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:57.19,sign_5367_37_Lullaby_at_Dawn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(486,682)}Raphtalia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:58.82,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:04.07,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,You lot would've died like dogs in the \Nwild if I hadn't taken you in back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:05.33,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:09.08,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think I've forgotten \Nthe atrocities you committed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.71,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:12.29,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I could never forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:14.63,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:16.17,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.34,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:21.30,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,This scumbag took Rifana-chan and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:25.93,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,No! Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:29.81,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:35.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Will killing him help you get closure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:38.78,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just with the sword, right? \NHaven't you grown stronger in other ways?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:53.92,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You're a terrible person who put so many \Ndemi-humans through hell, then killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.67,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I can never forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.17,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But if I kill you now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:02.88,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be any different from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:07.30,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,So I won't take your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:11.73,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You will live and atone for \Nthe sins you have committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.48,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Confound you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.98,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Know your place, scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:34.12,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:38.04,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Demis don't deserve to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:50.10,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Idol-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:51.31,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Idol-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.93,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Idol-sama is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:53.81,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.27,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.27,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.27,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:02.03,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:03.61,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:04.95,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.78,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:09.58,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Shield Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.79,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:15.12,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Reichnott! Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:16.25,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:17.75,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,First Aqua Heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.76,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take this chance to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:23.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:26.09,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But first...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:31.89,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Idol imprisoned his demi-human \Nslaves underground,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.18,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,and tortured them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:35.89,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:39.90,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:47.07,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too late to turn back, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.20,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need. I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:57.08,flashbackitalics,RMom,0000,0000,0000,,Always keep smiling and \Nplay nice with the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:59.12,flashbackitalics,RDad,0000,0000,0000,,And smile even more in hard times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:03.46,flashback,RDad,0000,0000,0000,,You must smile and help everyone \Naround you smile, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:08.30,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Dad... Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.72,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,I won't cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.85,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.69,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:27.57,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,We're still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.49,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll keep on living!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:34.12,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,As survivors, let's rebuild our village, \Nso it's the way it used to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:38.00,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that's what everyone \Nwho died would want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.04,flashback,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.67,flashback,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia-chan's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:46.80,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:48.42,flashback,VilA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:50.05,flashback,VilB,0000,0000,0000,,Let's rebuild our village!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.56,flashback,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:06.03,flashback,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,Your parents died, right? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:09.07,flashback,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.74,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,I am sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.58,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:20.66,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Dad said I should keep smiling in hard times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:24.42,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,If you're trying so hard \Nwith a smile on your face,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.09,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,I should do my best, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.13,flashback,Bo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.05,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:31.13,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.10,flashback,VilC,0000,0000,0000,,Help from the capital?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:35.97,flashback,VilD,0000,0000,0000,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.90,flashback,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Get on already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.90,flashback,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Quit wasting time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.70,flashback,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:53.82,flashback,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Get in, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.97,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Mel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:17.93,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:27.15,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia was trapped in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:31.49,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to see what was happening here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:34.07,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Just thinking about it makes me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:46.66,flashback,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.34,flashback,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,You bore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.76,flashback,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Scream and cry more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:08.23,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Rifana-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:18.16,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up, Rifana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:25.91,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'm sure the \NShield Hero will save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.34,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Rifana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.60,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,You're burning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:49.52,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you remember that flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:56.61,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,It was a symbol of how we demi-humans \Nwere allowed to build a village for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.62,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:00.82,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:04.16,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:07.12,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:09.00,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:19.76,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:26.02,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.44,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go back to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:34.15,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:36.44,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home to our village together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:38.65,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:44.66,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:53.25,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I couldn't make it any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.29,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:57.72,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:09.02,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Rifana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.48,flashback,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:15.86,flashback,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:26.45,flashback,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,You're being sold off to a slave merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:29.20,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,What about Rifana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:31.12,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:33.46,flashback,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,She's the only one being sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:34.46,flashback,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:35.96,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,What about Rifana-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:38.80,flashback,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,She's done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:53.53,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,...le... when times are tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:56.61,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:59.49,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,How do I smile again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:17.84,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,There's a survivor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.51,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:31.06,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:33.14,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:34.35,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.82,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone over here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:59.29,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Keel-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.38,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Keel-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:05.59,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.64,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,Who... are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:12.35,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You were brought here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:15.94,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:27.16,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:29.78,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget? It's me, Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:31.49,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.20,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.79,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.04,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:39.04,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:41.92,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That one time, you went \Ndiving and nearly drowned,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:44.17,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,and Sadeena-oneechan had to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:48.93,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You ate a poisonous mushroom and ended \Nup with an upset stomach another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:53.89,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You were in pain and begged me not to tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:58.15,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,And when I said we should rebuild \Nthe village after the Wave,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:00.98,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,you were the first one to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:05.40,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.45,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.83,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,It's really you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.16,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:15.66,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so grateful that you're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.50,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:23.84,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with the Shield Hero right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.88,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,What? The... Shield Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:31.47,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The Shield Hero is here to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.10,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.77,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,He's real...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:45.82,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,The Shield Hero really exists!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:48.08,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:50.70,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.49,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:56.49,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,Rifana-chan would've been \Nso happy to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:58.08,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Keel-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:00.50,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Rifana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:02.21,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Is she also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.50,flashbackitalics,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Raphtalia-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:12.97,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the Shield \NHero will come to save us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:15.56,flashbackitalics,R,0000,0000,0000,,I know he will!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.47,flashbackitalics,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.06,flashbackitalics,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,See him and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:20.44,flashbackitalics,R,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.57,flashback,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,Have him make me his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:02.19,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:06.90,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe such monstrous \Ndeeds were being done in Melromarc.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:08.98,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,Melty-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:13.91,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,As much as I hate to say it, similar \Nthings happen all across this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:15.41,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:18.87,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we needed Seyaette.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.04,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:25.08,flashback,Mirelia,0000,0000,0000,,Melty, I need you to do something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:27.29,flashback,Mirelia,0000,0000,0000,,Return to the capital
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:31.84,flashback,Mirelia,0000,0000,0000,,and admonish the king for \Nhis unjust treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:35.89,flashback,Mirelia,0000,0000,0000,,Ordinarily, I would go myself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:41.82,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:45.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia, who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:47.02,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Rifana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:51.78,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,She was gentler and more graceful than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:57.62,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,and she'd always say she wanted to \Nmeet you... meet the Shield Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:03.25,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give her and the \Nothers a proper send-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:05.46,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,They can't rest in peace \Nin a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:07.92,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.21,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:14.34,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't protect anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:18.10,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Before meeting you, I was powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.31,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:25.52,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,If only I was stronger, \NI could've kept everyone safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:27.19,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,They could have...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:30.27,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,You did protect us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:33.53,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't come to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:36.24,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,I probably would've died here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:43.00,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,And the only reason everyone hung in \Nthere without losing hope was your smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:46.00,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,We decided to keep smiling, \Nno matter how bad things got!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:47.33,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:51.09,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Keel-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:55.30,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I can't smile like I used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:57.68,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:02.68,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up killing someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.35,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:11.07,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It was all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:14.82,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I've done so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.99,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It was all a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:18.57,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:20.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:23.54,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the right to walk beside you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.04,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You did nothing wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.79,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:33.38,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I would've run from this world \Nwithout ever trusting anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:44.01,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you believed in me \Nback then that I'm here right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:46.73,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,that I got to meet Filo and Melty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:50.35,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It can't have been a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:55.82,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you were so tiny,\N and now you've met the Shield Hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:19:01.20,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,become such a cool lady, \Nand come back to save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:03.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:07.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who kept those kids alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.08,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:13.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:20.59,main,Keel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Rifana-chan's happy she \Ngot to meet the Shield Hero, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:24.35,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, we have to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:28.60,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure nobody goes through \Nwhat you and she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:31.85,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why you fought \Nwith me for all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:38.07,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Together with me, the Shield Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:45.66,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:52.88,main,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:55.38,main,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the Shield Hero's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.84,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You must be jealous, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:01.88,main,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:08.47,main,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.56,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:15.06,main,Rif,0000,0000,0000,,And one day, let's go back \Nto a village with that flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:15.90,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:32.54,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Rifana-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:37.25,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I'll bring back \Nthe flag from those days...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.67,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Together with Naofumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:52.69,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:55.73,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,In order to take you back,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:57.73,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,demi-humans from your \Ndomain are rioting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:59.90,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Go let them know you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:00.86,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:03.74,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:06.03,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Look there, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:15.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:17.54,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,O Supreme God,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:20.38,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,grant me the power to rend the Devil asunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:23.34,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,No... Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:24.47,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:28.86,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,The heroes of the past built that \Nstone monument to seal a monster away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:32.03,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,Is he trying to release that seal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:38.21,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Go on and destroy everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:40.11,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,You are free from your confines now, beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:43.25,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Bring divine judgment down \Nupon the Devil of the Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.83,0:21:49.09,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can stop me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:51.00,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,If I can kill the Devil of the Shield,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:54.51,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,I will be eternally blessed by God!
